HEADWORD: Trimestrial
<hw>Tri*mes"tri*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to a trimester, or period of three months; occurring once in
every three months; quarterly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

